<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Reset Password</title>
  <style>
    /* Add your CSS styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      max-width: 150px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .reset-link {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
        <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dwxly1dc7/image/upload/v1690709239/8838572ba14d424fac2b9eabdcc3215e_zhghil.png" alt="AceWears Logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>You recently requested to reset your password for your account at Ace Wears.</p>
      <p>Please click on the link below to update your password:</p>
      <a class="reset-link" href="https://acewears.co.ke/update-password">Reset Password</a>
      <p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br> Ace Wears Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
